text: Alexandrian is either: * An adjective referring to a place called Alexandria, as in Alexandrian text-type * A person from and/or inhabiting a city called Alexandria * A member of a group of Alexandrians, equally associated with Alexandria, as an Ancient school of theologians * A regional stage in the Silurian geological period ==See also== *Alexandrine (disambiguation) *Alexandrian Wicca
title: Alexandrian
